text:
Today was also smooth, wasn't it?
Good job.

Madoka never loses her pace even when
the environment changes. She's reliable.
Because the things to do remain unchanged.

That person has been dressing the same since I was
a child. Some things change, some things don't, huh?

Yeah,
I always feel reassured watching Fuyuko.

In that sense, I meant it.
...Well, never mind.
